üö® ATTENTION E-COMMERCE FOUNDERS üö®

If you're like the majority of DTC E-Commerce brands then you're probably feeling the pinch right now.

Ad costs are rising by the day.

Conversion rates are on the decline.

Cart abandonment rates are at an all-time high.

And email open rates are at an all-time low.

And let‚Äôs not even mention the tariffs, oh the tariffs.

The list just goes on and on‚Ä¶

And to make it even worse, every single day more and more competitors enter the market who are trying to steal your customers right from under your nose.

It's hard not to feel like the odds are stacked against you.

The reality is that most DTC E-Commerce brands are struggling to acquire customers PROFITABLY in today‚Äôs market, especially with paid ads, and if they don‚Äôt fix this issue asap they are looking down the barrel or bankruptcy in the next 6-12 months.

You see, most E-Commerce businesses fail NOT because they don't have a great product, service, story, or brand‚Ä¶

They fail because they get too busy running the business and never get the chance to sit down and optimize their entire sales funnel holistically and end up running traffic to a suboptimal store that leaks sales left and right which robs them of their profit margins and makes it impossible to scale.

And to make it worse, they end up hiring unqualified ‚Äúagencies‚Äù, ‚Äúgurus‚Äù, and ‚Äúexperts‚Äù who simply don‚Äôt have the broad expertise and real world experience to help them fix this issue and end up flushing even more $$$ down the drain.

The result‚Ä¶

Low ROAS numbers that barely cover their costs‚Ä¶

Ad campaigns that won‚Äôt scale profitably‚Ä¶

Mounting overheads‚Ä¶ 

‚Ä¶and constant stress, anxiety, and uncertainty.

But what if I was to tell you that there is a solution.

An optimization framework and proven protocol you can use to 2X your sales conversions in under 6 weeks flat‚Ä¶

A framework that has already been iterated and tested on more than 70 brands across 17 different product categories and 14 different counties spanning over 4 continents in the past 12 months alone.

But more importantly, a framework that has unlocked over 108% growth on average in the first 21 days for the brands who have implemented it.

A framework that has taken brands that came in doing a couple of hundred thousand per year to 8-figures in under 10 months.

A framework that has taken brands that were trending downwards year over year and got them back on track to positive growth in a matter of weeks.

A framework that has taken brands from over a million dollars in debt (ouch) and turned them into hyper-profitable cash generating machines that have investors lining up.

A framework that doesn‚Äôt rely on the latest ‚Äútactic‚Äù, ‚Äúhack‚Äù, or ‚Äústrategy‚Äù that works today and is dead by lunchtime tomorrow‚Ä¶

A framework that doesn't involve hoping, praying, or sheer luck.

But a data-driven approach to growth that gives you predictability in your marketing for once and for all and allows you to scale at your own pace and on your own terms.

A systematic, holistic methodology that is the result of more than 25 years in the trenches working with some of the best known E-Commerce brands in the world such as Canon, Tommy Hilfiger, Ashley Stewart, and many more.

My name is Sabir Semerkant and I call this framework ‚ÄúRapid 2X‚Ñ¢Ô∏è‚Äù.

...and if you are an E-Commerce founder who is struggling to scale profitably then this might just be the answer to your prayers.

Rapid 2X is a holistic optimization framework I developed to help early stage Ecommerce brands maximize their sales conversions so they can scale profitably and unlock growth potential that most founders don't even know is there for the taking.

Growth that is hidden in plain sight, camouflaged beneath all of the mess and complexity that goes hand in hand with running an e-commerce business.

Ads, landing pages, upsells, downsells, crosssells, email flows, loyalty programs, etc.

It‚Äôs enough to make your head spin.

You need everything to be optimized across the entire chain if you want to compete for business in today‚Äôs hyper competitive market, especially if you are using paid ads, and the reality is that most brands are optimized to a 6/10 at best.

But imagine what it would feel like to unlock that additional growth for your brand?

To see your ROAS numbers increase by 50-150%.

To go to bed every single night safe and secure knowing that you have the correct systems in place that are working for you around the clock on autopilot to suck in your ideal customers and squeeze out every last sale from your advertising dollars and maximize your ROAS.

To wake up to a dashboard with tens or even hundreds of new orders every single morning.

To be in complete control and have the ability to grow your sales with predictability while maximizing your margins regardless of what is happening in the market.

What would that mean for your brand?

Or more importantly, what would this mean for you and your entire company?

More revenue.
More profits.

More exposure.

More influence.

More investment.

More fun.

Probably.

Less stress.

Less anxiety.

Less uncertainty.

Fewer arguments.

Surely.

But more than anything, this methodology gives you the one thing that every business owner on the planet wants...

More FREEDOM.

The freedom to grow your brand ON YOUR TERMS.

The freedom to invest in long-term strategies that will yield even bigger returns down the road.

The freedom to think big and stop worrying about just getting by.

The freedom to THRIVE.

No more hoping and praying that your marketing dollars produce a ROAS above breakeven.

No more relying on Uncle Facebook and Aunt Google to bring home the bacon so you can pay your staff.

No more feeling like you are rolling the dice every single month and crossing your fingers that this isn't the month when the wheels fall off and it all goes horribly wrong.
Just complete clarity and confidence that your brand is on the right track with the right strategies in place to grow PROFITABLY.

Here are just a few of my success stories to date using this method:

‚úÖ Ashley Stewart from 3M - 30M in under 2 years

‚úÖ The Vitamin Shoppe from 12M - 55M in 4.5 years

üî• In the past 12 months alone I helped more than 70 E-Commerce brands across 17 different product categories grow by an average of 108% in under 21 days by implementing this framework.

üëâ Brands like The Aurum Brothers, a Netherlands based men's jewelry brand, who felt like they had tried everything after working with multiple experts and were stuck at 1.5M for more than 2 years with mounting debt who experienced a 146% increase in sales in the first 21 days, hit 3M within 10 months, and are now on track to hit 7M.

üëâ Brands like global luxury luggage company Globe Trotter who experienced a 334% increase in conversions across all 3 of their international stores in under 30 days

üëâ Brands like women‚Äôs water-sports and professional swimwear business, Wallien, who saw an 88% increase in sales in under 30 days.

In fact, I have more than 50 independent reviews from DTC E-Commerce founders from all over the world operating in every category known to man who swear by this framework.

Click below to learn more‚Ä¶

What do you have to lose?
